  <main id="main" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Do you store my writing?</h3><p>No. Input is processed locally for the session and then deleted. You can trigger <em>Delete Now</em> any time.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Do you train on my content?</h3><p>Never. We do not use user content to train models.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Do I need an account?</h3><p>No. v1 does not require login.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Can I run this offline?</h3><p>Yes, when the backend is hosted locally.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Do you track users?</h3><p>No tracking pixels. Minimal, anonymous operational logs only when required; opt-out available.</p></div>

      <h2>Using the Product</h2>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>What file types can I upload?</h3><p>TXT, MD, DOCX, and text-based PDFs. You can also paste text directly.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>How long does analysis take?</h3><p>Usually seconds for texts under ~5,000 words on typical hardware.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>What insights do I get in v1?</h3><p>Keywords & themes, a sentiment overview with a short explanation, word count, and a preview snippet.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Is there a comparison view?</h3><p>Yes. Compare two texts side-by-side and see a combined chart.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>How accurate are the insights?</h3><p>They are guides, not verdicts—use them to prompt reflection.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Any size limits?</h3><p>Very large files may be truncated or rejected for stability.</p></div>

      <h2>Export & Deletion</h2>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>What can I export?</h3><p>PDF (one-page summary) or JSON (structured data).</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Can I control deletion?</h3><p>Yes—choose <em>Delete Now</em> or let auto-delete run after analysis/export.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>What does the JSON include?</h3><p>File name, word count, preview HTML, keywords, sentiment, optional emotions, and a deletion timestamp.</p></div>

      <h2>Accessibility & Support</h2>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Is the interface accessible?</h3><p>Keyboard navigation, alt text for charts, and a high-contrast option are included.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>How do I report a bug or request a feature?</h3><p>Email support with steps to reproduce and a small non-sensitive sample.</p></div>

      <h2>Technical & Reliability</h2>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>What if I close the tab?</h3><p>A backend cleanup task purges temporary data shortly after interruption.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Cloud storage?</h3><p>Not in v1. Download exports locally.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Which models do you use?</h3><p>A controlled NLP pipeline focused on speed and privacy.</p></div>

      <h2>Pricing & Terms</h2>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Is it free?</h3><p>Pricing will be announced with the public release. Pilot access may be free for testers.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><h3>Terms of use?</h3><p>Use responsibly. Do not upload unlawful content or sensitive personal data.</p></div>
    </div>
  </main>

